 Amit Yadav , 20 , was driving his red Honda Civic up to 25 miles over the speed limit when he lost control and smashed into an oncoming Renault Cleo in August 2013 .
His two passengers - brothers Haider , and Taimur Kayani , 17 , were killed in the collision .
Yadav denied two charges of causing death by dangerous driving and dangerous driving .